## Git and worktree requirements

The system should use Git worktrees for isolation.

Design an MVP approach where:

* every task has an integration branch
* the first version uses one implementation worktree
* later specialist agents may receive separate worktrees
* the orchestrator creates, inspects, and removes worktrees
* agents cannot push directly
* agents cannot run destructive Git commands
* approved commits can be applied to the integration branch
* dirty worktrees are detected
